ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>這時保方戴巴拿，已與施丹的牙朗拆到二百招以上。兩隊踢法家數截然不同，但均是愈鬥力氣愈長，球影腳風，籠蓋了卡迪夫之頂，球迷叫上來的聲音直攻入領隊二人耳中。祖記雖無拉莫斯，始終不落下風。施丹激鬥中覺得卡斯米路微微搖晃，心知433陣法為希古恩衝擊，頃刻間便要倒台，那時勢必和巴塞、皇迷同歸於盡，又見屌帥戰術越變越奇，再鬥百餘招只怕便要為祖記所制</blockquote>"},{"pid":"83bcc7e859ed890822959616a83e9de3329c741b","tid":268340,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"踢完先開post啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"32652d697c23d11d510b1d5ede5ee4dc6b66b40c","tid":268340,"uid":19660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踢完先開post啦傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗騰到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df33f9cbe3a24d2ce4ca4d538e7d4befe15ad3dc","tid":268340,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>踢完先開post啦傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗騰到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n騰乜撚<br />\n贏都未贏就開post<br />\n咁撚好野上年唔開定今季贏西甲嘅post？<br />\n多鳩餘"},{"pid":"a3aec9faf5ddcd0c132a5ec59478680875c81777","tid":268340,"uid":18669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>踢完先開post啦傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗騰到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n騰乜撚<br />\n贏都未贏就開post<br />\n咁撚好野上年唔開定今季贏西甲嘅post？<br />\n多鳩餘</blockquote><br />\n對獌狗唔洗咁認真"},{"pid":"6dfd645239d13e7592e758515484a1ea773fa609","tid":268340,"uid":53543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>踢完先開post啦傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗騰到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n騰乜撚<br />\n贏都未贏就開post<br />\n咁撚好野上年唔開定今季贏西甲嘅post？<br />\n多鳩餘</blockquote><br />\n好明顯蝦腸啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm